Quickstrike:






Quickstrike opened his eyes, hearing two female voices. He quickly dimed his 
optics as his head rushed. He groaned deeply. Besides the pain in his head, 
he wasn't in a very comfortable position. He leaned over, and nearly lost 
his balance, despite being seated. He put his legs out to the side which 
made things a little better.

"Tarnation," he mumbled while opening his eyes again. He saw Stingtra and 
KitKat. He struggled to stand up and get his balance. He stepped out leaned 
heavily on the side of the chamber. He held his head.

"Ah got th' worst headache and ah'm dizzy," he mumbled. "Tired too." he 
added. He felt like he was going to pass out. "Ah'm gonna lie down." He 
walked off into the main section of the room.
